=====  BRICK  ===============================================================
=====  a scoreboard website and web service for the November Games  =========
=====  (c) triode  2009-2021  triode@ftso.net  all rights reversed  =========

To import a directory full of scores, do:

    RAILS_ENV=production bundle exec rails c
    irb> Season[2021].import_scores_dir('data/scores/2021')

Add the year to the top of app/views/layouts/application.html.haml,
then `touch tmp/restart.txt`.
